title: Zoo Walkthrough 2 — Aviary and Gift Shop
story: friendly-zoo
description: Chained full-playthrough, chapter 2 of 5. The parrot's cycling flavor with the once-only aside, cycle position surviving save/restore (absorbs the old wt-05 choice-cycle proof, ADR-196 C2), and the camera pickup. Continues from wt-01.
---

# Into the aviary (visit score) — the parrot notices new arrivals.
> west
[OK: contains "Aviary"]
[OK: contains "The parrot ruffles its feathers and eyes you with interest"]

# Examine 1 — cycle variant 0 + the first-time aside.
> examine parrot
[OK: contains "whistles a jaunty tune"]
[OK: contains "rescues from the illegal pet trade"]

# Examine 2 — cycle variant 1; the once-only aside is gone.
> examine parrot
[OK: contains "Pretty bird"]
[OK: not contains "rescues from the illegal pet trade"]

# Save with the cycle counter at 2.
$save parrot-mid

# Examine 3 — cycle variant 2. Turn 10: the two-hour PA rides this turn.
> examine parrot
[OK: contains "theatrical disdain"]
[OK: contains "Two hours until closing"]

# Restore: the world (and its textState counter) goes back to 2.
$restore parrot-mid

# Resumes at variant 2 — the counter persisted in the save (AC-8).
# The engine turn marches on through a restore while the world's
# sequence pointers rewind, so the replayed two-hour PA and the first
# feeding call both ride this turn.
> examine parrot
[OK: contains "theatrical disdain"]
[OK: not contains "whistles a jaunty tune"]
[OK: contains "FEEDING TIME"]

# West to the gift shop (visit score).
> west
[OK: contains "Gift Shop"]
[OK: contains "disposable camera"]

> take camera
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> examine pins
[OK: contains "costs more than it should"]

> east
[OK: contains "Aviary"]
